data.Name: Del Paxton
data.Bio: Del Paxton are an American alternative rock band from Buffalo, New York. The band consists of vocalist/guitarist Dylan England (formerly of Longitude), vocalist/bassist Zach Schoedel (formerly of Fairway) and drummer Greg McClure (formerly of Beach Parade). The band formed in 2013; and are named after the fictional jazz pianist portrayed by Bill Cobbs in the 1996 film That Thing You Do! They played their first show in May 2013 in Fredonia, New York.
